title: Lunar Revel 2016
body: Does anyone know when this will come to Oceania? I mean the 26th of January is today right? Can't wait for skins!

replies.body: It hasn't started on NA yet either. Despite OCE getting new content first, Events are still dictated by NA time (more specifically, the PST Time Zone). While the skins themselves are already available in the store, the event itself should kick off no later than mid-morning tomorrow.
Skins are already in the store
